你问下次live时会表演吗？\n嗯——兰是说过想要把这首歌加进节目单，\n演出的可能性应该很高吧","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"memorial130-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"巴","body":"对了对了，前阵子我们还一起听过这首歌呢。\n就是我们以前第一次录这首歌的CD","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"memorial130-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"巴","body":"真是太令人怀念了。\n所以我今天决定把当时的乐谱拿来，\n让大家一起演奏一下这首歌","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"simizimi01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"memorial130-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"巴","body":"我觉得，我们现在和以前的演奏肯定会截然不同。\n不仅发挥的稳定性完全不同，也很明白应该在什么时候煽动气氛","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"memorial130-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"巴","body":"我在听以前的演奏时可是吓了一跳哦。\n心里一直在想，诶？这是我演奏的吗？"